data.description: New Price!!! Country living at its best.  Spacious triple wide with a full daylight basement on 7+ acres. Three bedrooms, 2.5 baths, large master suite, living room, dining room and family room, all on the main floor.  Partially finished daylight basement doubles the square footage. Great option for multiple or extended family use. In the midst of unlimited recreational activities and wildlife, this home is paradise for outdoor enthusiasts. Walking distance to amazing Columbia Gorge viewing area, hiking and biking trails.
